heronarts.lx.modulator
Class Click

java.lang.Object
  heronarts.lx.modulator.LXModulator
      heronarts.lx.modulator.Click

public class Click
extends LXModulator

A click is a simple modulator that fires a value of 1 every time its duration has passed. Otherwise it always returns 0.
